The survey respondents provide a range of answers regarding the percentage of their organization's inside sales that represents the carton sales category, as well as their participation in carton sales and packing.

According to the survey results, there are 27 organizations currently involved in carton sales and packing. However, 4 of the respondents indicated that their level of interest was very low, while 1 person reported having no interest in the activity and a fourth did not answer.
